title: Cyndi Lauper - Twelve Deadly Cyns... And Then Some (1994)
description:
Twelve Deadly Cyns...and Then Some is Cyndi Lauper's greatest hits CD, released in 1994.Its greatest sales success was in Japan where it went 5x Platinum. Its greatest chart success was in the United Kingdom where it reached #2 on the charts spending almost nine months on chart, eventually going double platinum selling almost 600,000 copies. In the USA it reached gold status. The album would go on to sell over 6 million copies worldwide.
